name: Son of Doge
description: "Son of Doge first and foremost is a community driven project with the sole task of protecting the community, this is achieved by providing a safe environment for all. We aim to be an integral component to the BSC (Binance Smart Chain) stack of applications. The team behind Son of Doge aims to innovate the BSC by building a project which provides a safe area for investor research, and a fun, entertaining and especially rewarding experience for everyone involved. Each trade has a small fee deducted to pay for marketing ventures and the further development of the Son of Doge ecosystem. These ventures are critical, as they allow Son of Doge to reach potential technology and marketing partners to further develop and grow the Son of Doge ecosystem."
